---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Contact Bright Horizon | Get Started Today"
  description="Reach out to Bright Horizon for cloud hosting, Odoo ERP, automation, IT consulting, and managed business technology solutions in South Africa. Response within 1 business day."
>
<section class="soft-gradient border-b border-[#1F7A63]/10">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20">
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] lg:items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="animate-fade-up text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#175247]">Contact Bright Horizon</p>
        <h1 class="animate-fade-up animate-delay-1 mt-4 max-w-3xl text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-[#103B34] md:text-6xl">
          Let's build something that grows with your business.
        </h1>
        <p class="animate-fade-up animate-delay-2 mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-[#1A1A1A]/80">
          Share your challenge or goal — whether it's reducing costs, modernising systems, automating operations, or launching on the cloud. We'll come back with clarity, not a sales pitch.
        </p>
        <div class="animate-fade-up animate-delay-3 mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/contact/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="btn-primary btn-shine inline-flex rounded-full px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold">
            Email Our Team
          </a>
          <a href="tel:+27821234567" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[#1F7A63]/35 bg-white/80 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-[#145A46] shadow-sm transition hover:bg-white hover:border-[#1F7A63]/55 active:scale-95">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M22 16.92V19a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6A19.79 19.79 0 0 1 2.12 3.18 2 2 0 0 1 4.11 1h2.09a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.12.9.33 1.79.63 2.65a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.41 8.41a16 16 0 0 0 8.18 8.18l.93-.93a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.86.3 1.75.51 2.65.63A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
            </svg>
            Call Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section-shell animate-fade-up p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Why Clients Reach Out</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-1">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20 bg-white/70 p-5">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#103B34]">Reduce Costs & Improve Efficiency</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/75">Automate manual processes, consolidate systems, and cut operational overhead with the right technology stack.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20 bg-white/70 p-5">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#103B34]">Modernise Business Systems</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/75">ERP implementation, cloud migration, and systems integration that replace fragmented tools with one connected platform.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20 bg-white/70 p-5">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#103B34]">Secure & Grow with Confidence</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/75">Cyber resilience, governance, POPIA compliance, and security controls that protect your business as you scale.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20 bg-white/70 p-5">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#103B34]">Practical SME Technology</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/75">Flexible packages designed to give growing businesses enterprise-grade operations without enterprise complexity.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20 bg-white/70 p-5">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#103B34]">Strategic IT Planning</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/75">Roadmaps, technology audits, and advisory from experienced practitioners who understand your business as well as the technology.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16">
  <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr]">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="section-shell p-7">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Direct Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/75">Book a consultation session or reach us directly by phone, WhatsApp, or email.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/80">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#6A4917]">Consultation</p>
            <a
              href="/contact/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
              class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[#C79C49]/40 px-5 py-2.5 font-semibold text-[#175247] transition hover:bg-[#F8EFD8]"
            >
              Book a Consultation
            </a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#6A4917]">Mobile / WhatsApp</p>
            <a href="tel:+27821234567" class="mt-2 inline-block text-base font-semibold text-[#175247] hover:text-[#103B34]">+27 82 123 4567</a>
            <a href="https://wa.me/27821234567" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-[#25D366] px-5 py-2.5 font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#1FAE53]">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
              </svg>
              Chat Now
            </a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#6A4917]">Telephone</p>
            <a href="tel:+27821234567" class="mt-2 inline-block text-base font-semibold text-[#175247] hover:text-[#103B34]">+27 82 123 4567</a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#6A4917]">Email</p>
            <a href="mailto:info@brighthorizon.co.za" class="mt-2 inline-block text-base font-semibold text-[#175247] hover:text-[#103B34]">info@brighthorizon.co.za</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section-shell p-7">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Availability</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/80">We engage on a flexible basis, with structured availability aligned to client needs and time zones across Africa and beyond. Priority engagements and cross-border coordination can be arranged by appointment.</p>
        <div class="mt-5 rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20 bg-[#FFF9EF] p-5 text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/80">
          <p class="font-semibold text-[#103B34]">Response expectation</p>
          <p class="mt-2">Most enquiries receive an initial response within one business day.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl relative" style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0f3c34 0%, #175247 55%, #1a6358 100%); border: 1px solid rgba(199,156,73,0.25); box-shadow: 0 32px 72px -36px rgba(10,35,31,0.55); min-height: 460px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;">
      <!-- Gold top bar -->
      <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-1" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c79c49, rgba(199,156,73,0.25));"></div>
      <!-- Decorative rings -->
      <div class="absolute pointer-events-none" style="top: -60px; right: -60px; width: 220px; height: 220px; border-radius: 50%; border: 1px solid rgba(199,156,73,0.08);"></div>
      <div class="absolute pointer-events-none" style="bottom: -40px; left: -40px; width: 160px; height: 160px; border-radius: 50%; border: 1px solid rgba(199,156,73,0.06);"></div>
      <div class="relative flex flex-col px-8 py-10 md:px-10">
        <!-- Eyebrow -->
        <div class="mb-5 inline-flex items-center self-start gap-2 rounded-full border border-[#C79C49]/30 px-3.5 py-1.5" style="background: rgba(199,156,73,0.12);">
          <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]" style="box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(199,156,73,0.6);"></span>
          <span class="text-[0.68rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#e1c178]">Take the First Step</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight text-[#fffaf1] md:text-4xl">The form takes <span style="color: #e1c178;">60 seconds.</span> The impact can last years.</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 h-0.5 w-12 rounded-full" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c79c49, rgba(199,156,73,0.15));"></div>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-sm text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(255,244,222,0.7);">
          Share your project brief, security challenge, or growth ambition. We route every message to the right person and respond with substance — not a template.
        </p>
        <!-- Trust micro-copy -->
        <div class="mt-3 mb-7 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-1">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[0.72rem]" style="color: rgba(255,244,222,0.45);"><span class="text-[#c79c49]">&#10003;</span> Confidential</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[0.72rem]" style="color: rgba(255,244,222,0.45);"><span class="text-[#c79c49]">&#10003;</span> No obligation</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[0.72rem]" style="color: rgba(255,244,222,0.45);"><span class="text-[#c79c49]">&#10003;</span> Response within 1 business day</span>
        </div>
        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="/contact/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-7 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold transition hover:opacity-90 active:scale-95"
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e4cb97 0%, #d5b577 58%, #c79c49 138%); color: #0f3c34; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px -8px rgba(199,156,73,0.5);"
          >
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
            Start the Conversation
          </a>
          <a
            href="/contact/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold transition hover:bg-[rgba(199,156,73,0.1)] active:scale-95"
            style="border-color: rgba(199,156,73,0.4); color: #ffe9bc;"
          >
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
            Book a Consultation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</MainLayout>
